Basic :
1.  Game board should not be till 100 -  should be customizable
2.  it should allow more than 2 players
3.  snake and ladder loop should not be there
4.  snakes and ladder can also be randomized ->  small | medium | large | superLarge [  factory pattern ]
    randomizing criteria :
         small snake | ladder -> 20% of the size decrease | increase
         medium  snake | ladder ->  40 % of the size decrease | increase
         large  snake | ladder -> 60 % of the size decrease | increase
         superLarge snake | ladder -> 80 % of the size decrease | increase
5.  size should be a multiple of 10
6. should allow more things to be added like snake and ladder
